{"tid":1937942,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"眾志成城抗肺炎*醫者父母心","createTime":"2020-03-22T08:27:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T12:47:56.000Z","uid":323891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8694a2347c33c7eff84ac4e844daf273d1e44200","tid":1937942,"uid":323891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T08:27:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XVu74biwC84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXVu74biwC84&d=HaOdbOSPDN3vR1kWeckjcBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=9468d5f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XVu74biwC84</a><br />\n<br />\n陳以誠醫生 2003 年創作這首抗肺炎歌，大家聽完覺得好好笑，17 年後，歌曲重編重唱，完全是另一種感受。<br />\n<br />\n歌曲最後一句「建立信心，在香港」，17 年前聽，覺得很老土；但在今時今日聽到這句，覺得很觸動，今天，還有幾多人，會唱一句這樣本土的歌詞？"},{"pid":"f03b813baca089352c6d7dde7bd964e4b02af073","tid":1937942,"uid":32213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T08:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07db02211e3e164dff83a454dd75a1995ba11b91","tid":1937942,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T12:47:56.000Z","msg":"當年膠歌"}]}